 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Class E hard hats + FR shirts for the full electrical trade kit.</p>
 </a>
 <a href="/industries/data-center-contractors-las-vegas/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
